1
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,660 --> 00:00:55,580
=Episode 21=

3
00:00:56,799 --> 00:00:57,759
Jing Liuli,

4
00:00:58,560 --> 00:00:59,479
it's been a while.

5
00:01:00,039 --> 00:01:02,039
I heard you were kicked out for a while.

6
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:05,000
You dare show your face here again?

7
00:01:10,079 --> 00:01:10,760
Who are you?

8
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:12,079
I'm not Jing Liuli.

9
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:13,120
Stop pretending!

10
00:01:13,439 --> 00:01:14,200
You wretched maid.

11
00:01:14,599 --> 00:01:15,799
In this vast palace,

12
00:01:15,959 --> 00:01:16,959
everyone knows Jing Liuli

13
00:01:17,079 --> 00:01:19,480
only gained favor because she resembled
the former Princess.

14
00:01:20,239 --> 00:01:21,280
You said you're not Jing Liuli,

15
00:01:21,959 --> 00:01:24,879
have you come up with
some new games to win favor?

16
00:01:24,959 --> 00:01:26,640
I don't know what you're talking about,

17
00:01:27,239 --> 00:01:28,400
but you're rude,

18
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:29,519
and you look nasty.

19
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:31,640
Go back to wherever you came from.

20
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:33,079
After all these days,

21
00:01:33,719 --> 00:01:35,640
you have changed so drastically.

22
00:01:36,319 --> 00:01:38,920
This must be your true nature.

23
00:01:39,359 --> 00:01:41,439
Looking at your haughty
and overbearing ways,

24
00:01:41,599 --> 00:01:43,680
I'd say you've harmed quite a few.

25
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:45,719
This slap

26
00:01:45,959 --> 00:01:47,280
is to discipline you
on behalf of your parents

27
00:01:47,439 --> 00:01:48,519
and to serve justice.

28
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:51,359
Jing Liuli,

29
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,239
are you insane?

30
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,560
My father is the Prime Minister!

31
00:01:56,519 --> 00:01:57,640
I couldn't care less!

32
00:01:57,799 --> 00:01:58,879
The slaps are all you get today.

33
00:01:58,959 --> 00:01:59,560
Provoke me again,

34
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:02,359
and I'll tear you apart!

35
00:02:04,879 --> 00:02:05,560
No way!

36
00:02:07,319 --> 00:02:08,000
No way!

37
00:02:08,719 --> 00:02:09,639
You're not Jing Liuli.

38
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,199
Where's your birthmark?

39
00:02:14,719 --> 00:02:15,400
This scar...

40
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:19,599
I thought you'd never
play the zither again.

41
00:02:20,599 --> 00:02:22,319
I never expected
you to win the King's sympathy,

42
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:25,159
and he even found you
the Nine-section Sweet Flag!

43
00:02:27,479 --> 00:02:28,000
Could it be

44
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,360
that you've been taken over?

45
00:02:32,479 --> 00:02:33,360
Who are you, really?

46
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,800
Forget about who I am.

47
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,520
You've got bigger problems of your own.

48
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:40,080
Snapping at everyone like a mad dog,

49
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:42,719
you've made countless enemies!

50
00:02:42,879 --> 00:02:44,759
You're on the brink of disaster,
and you don't even realize it!

51
00:02:44,919 --> 00:02:46,360
I advise you to write some letters

52
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:47,719
to your Prime Minister father

53
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,719
and ask him to show you the way!

54
00:02:49,919 --> 00:02:51,599
Stop barking here.

55
00:02:51,759 --> 00:02:53,120
It's annoying!

56
00:02:54,719 --> 00:02:55,319
Mark my words,

57
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,879
your luck has run out!

58
00:02:59,639 --> 00:03:00,360
Yours too!

59
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:08,800
How does she

60
00:03:08,919 --> 00:03:10,680
know about the scar on my hand?

61
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:15,639
But this scene feels so familiar.

62
00:03:16,759 --> 00:03:17,680
Mu Ruyi,

63
00:03:19,039 --> 00:03:19,960
Jing Liuli,

64
00:03:20,719 --> 00:03:21,639
and I.

65
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,280
There's simply no way

66
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:26,240
there can be three people
who look exactly alike.

67
00:03:28,879 --> 00:03:30,199
Who am I, really?

68
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:36,000
Liuli this, Liuli that...

69
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,560
Who are you?

70
00:03:49,919 --> 00:03:50,439
Rushi.

71
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:57,120
Shattered glass blooms
like a broken dream.

72
00:03:58,039 --> 00:03:59,599
Cold rain on the windowpane

73
00:04:00,759 --> 00:04:02,960
severs the last strands of yearning.

74
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,319
I think Your Majesty

75
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:08,639
would much rather
hear Liuli recite poetry

76
00:04:09,159 --> 00:04:10,319
than listen to me.

77
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:18,839
You once said

78
00:04:19,839 --> 00:04:21,079
that she's just a person from the past.

79
00:04:22,399 --> 00:04:23,720
Only today did I learn

80
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:25,199
that this person from the past

81
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:28,480
turns out to be the one you dream of
day and night.

82
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:33,639
That's not true.

83
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:37,879
I look so much like Liuli,

84
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:41,079
so how does the Princess of Xiling
connect to me?

85
00:04:43,399 --> 00:04:44,439
Do you really think

86
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,720
"misunderstanding" covers all of this?

87
00:04:47,519 --> 00:04:49,319
Jing Liuli was just a court singer.

88
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:52,079
Why do you compare yourself to her?

89
00:04:54,759 --> 00:04:55,879
Then why do I have

90
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:58,600
the same scar on my hand as her?

91
00:04:59,639 --> 00:05:00,759
Does that mean I am her?

92
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,000
No, you are not.

93
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,639
You are no one's replacement.

94
00:05:07,639 --> 00:05:08,360
You are unique.

95
00:05:10,519 --> 00:05:11,680
We promised each other

96
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,319
that between us,

97
00:05:14,519 --> 00:05:15,439
we would leave the past behind

98
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:17,480
and only look to the future.

99
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,480
I thought I could do it.

100
00:05:21,399 --> 00:05:23,920
But Liuli's presence still lingers here.

101
00:05:24,519 --> 00:05:26,279
I can't ignore your shared past.

102
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,879
She will always come between us.

103
00:05:32,199 --> 00:05:33,560
I need some time to think.

104
00:05:36,519 --> 00:05:37,240
You may leave.

105
00:05:45,199 --> 00:05:45,959
Mother...

106
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:47,600
No...

107
00:05:49,879 --> 00:05:51,199
- Mother...
- My Lady! My Lady!

108
00:05:51,319 --> 00:05:51,959
No...

109
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:52,879
My Lady!

110
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:54,639
My Lady!

111
00:05:57,199 --> 00:05:57,800
My Lady!

112
00:05:58,439 --> 00:05:59,199
What happened?

113
00:06:08,519 --> 00:06:11,480
Shouldn't you be addressing me
"Your Highness" instead?

114
00:06:13,519 --> 00:06:14,279
My Lady,

115
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:15,439
what's happened to you?

116
00:06:15,759 --> 00:06:17,600
Did Ling Xiao say something to you?

117
00:06:18,519 --> 00:06:20,319
So it's exactly as I suspected.

118
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:23,639
I am the Princess of Xiling.

119
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:27,560
Jing Liuli, Mu Ruyi...

120
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,800
They were all me.

121
00:06:32,279 --> 00:06:34,600
I just couldn't remember anything.

122
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,480
Some memories

123
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,240
are better off buried.

124
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,279
Everything has already

125
00:06:42,879 --> 00:06:43,879
been fated.

126
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:45,759
If you don't tell me the truth,

127
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:48,399
I'll only suffer more

128
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,519
and keep living in doubt.

129
00:06:53,319 --> 00:06:54,160
Actually,

130
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:57,279
the past between you and Ling Xiao

131
00:06:59,319 --> 00:07:01,480
is what needs to be buried.

132
00:07:16,959 --> 00:07:19,160
Now that Your Majesty
remembers everything,

133
00:07:19,399 --> 00:07:20,319
do you still have headaches?

134
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,480
Mo Shuo, take a seat.

135
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:28,439
I think Ruyi has figured something out.

136
00:07:29,399 --> 00:07:29,959
Your Majesty,

137
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,360
don't dwell on it too much.

138
00:07:37,279 --> 00:07:38,399
What should I do

139
00:07:39,399 --> 00:07:40,800
to stop her suffering?

140
00:07:43,319 --> 00:07:44,839
Let me be the only one

141
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,959
to carry the pain of the past.

142
00:08:02,639 --> 00:08:03,199
Your Highness.

143
00:08:05,839 --> 00:08:07,319
Take it away. I won't drink it.

144
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:14,519
Your Highness,

145
00:08:15,279 --> 00:08:15,839
your health won't improve

146
00:08:15,959 --> 00:08:17,480
unless you take your medicine.

147
00:08:19,959 --> 00:08:20,759
Your Highness?

148
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:23,920
I am no longer a princess.

149
00:08:25,519 --> 00:08:27,800
I'm just a stray dog
locked in the palace,

150
00:08:28,279 --> 00:08:30,600
with no past to call my own.

151
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:33,720
Trust me,

152
00:08:34,519 --> 00:08:35,759
everything will be alright.

153
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:37,039
So,

154
00:08:37,879 --> 00:08:38,519
I am that former princess

155
00:08:38,639 --> 00:08:40,759
who was humiliated in every way.

156
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:44,159
I forgot all that hatred

157
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:45,960
and humiliation.

158
00:08:46,799 --> 00:08:48,519
I fell in love with the man
who killed my mother!

159
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:53,000
And now that I know the truth,

160
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:56,279
I still can't feel the pain
as if it were my own.

161
00:08:58,679 --> 00:08:59,679
Once you're better,

162
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,440
we'll leave the palace.

163
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:03,440
Do you really think
that leaving the palace

164
00:09:04,039 --> 00:09:05,919
will let us start fresh,

165
00:09:07,639 --> 00:09:09,559
as if nothing ever happened?

166
00:09:12,879 --> 00:09:13,600
Your Highness.

167
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:26,600
Rushi.

168
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:29,799
Finish your medicine today.

169
00:09:30,759 --> 00:09:31,399
Leave.

170
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:33,840
I don't want to see you again.

171
00:09:35,039 --> 00:09:36,159
And I won't take the medicine.

172
00:09:36,919 --> 00:09:37,639
Leave?

173
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:41,879
The entire palace is mine.

174
00:09:42,639 --> 00:09:44,840
And you, Liu Rushi,

175
00:09:45,279 --> 00:09:47,879
you are nothing but a tool I used.

176
00:09:49,279 --> 00:09:50,679
Indeed, Your Majesty.

177
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:53,840
You are the supreme ruler,

178
00:09:54,519 --> 00:09:55,840
master of the world.

179
00:09:56,759 --> 00:09:58,320
You can go wherever you wish,

180
00:09:58,879 --> 00:10:00,559
and toy with whomever you please.

181
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:02,519
Then I shall leave.

182
00:10:03,799 --> 00:10:04,559
Take the medicine

183
00:10:05,919 --> 00:10:07,440
or poisoned wine.

184
00:10:08,679 --> 00:10:09,879
The choice is yours.

185
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:26,840
Absolutely not, Your Majesty!

186
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,799
If Miss Mu took the Oblivion Herb again,

187
00:10:28,919 --> 00:10:29,399
I'm afraid...

188
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,240
There must be a way out.

189
00:10:30,799 --> 00:10:31,480
There must be a way to make her

190
00:10:31,559 --> 00:10:33,320
return to the carefree Mu Ruyi.

191
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:36,200
But she will lose more memories!

192
00:10:36,559 --> 00:10:38,720
She may even forget
everything around her!

193
00:10:39,039 --> 00:10:41,000
Nothing matters more than her life!

194
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,600
It doesn't matter who she remembers

195
00:10:42,639 --> 00:10:43,399
or who she forgets.

196
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:45,200
I only care that she lives.

197
00:10:46,879 --> 00:10:47,799
I understand.

198
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,919
But Miss Mu is bent on dying.

199
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:53,000
She won't take the medicine willingly.

200
00:10:54,159 --> 00:10:55,159
Then we'll have to find a way

201
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:57,759
to compel her.
